  Starshatter represents the next generation of space combat simulation 
  games. Starshatter extends the gameplay concepts of the classic sims by 
  combining fighter and starship combat in a single game. Starshatter also 
  integrates elements of real-time-strategy games by allowing fleet 
  commanders to direct the battle on a tactical level.
